{"tid":384588,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「梁粉」樓王叫港青睇遠啲 移民墨西哥印度買樓","createTime":"2017-09-02T12:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T13:04:47.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73782601c955fe07d80d379cb4fe9ef4ceba928f","tid":384588,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:16:11.000Z","msg":"特首林鄭月娥智囊、智庫組織「香港黃金50」創辦人林奮強接受電視訪問，被問到港人買不起樓怎辦時，直言除非政府增加土地供應，否則「唔好喺香港住咯，唔好喺香港發展咯」，應移居具發展潛力且住得愉快的地方，例如實際地到印度、墨西哥或越南等地買樓，便可從容地養妻活兒和退休，勸年輕人「要睇遠啲」。<br />\n<br />\n被視為「梁粉」的林奮強，有前「行會樓王」之稱，如今他指香港樓市問題禍害三代，坦言香港「唔係一個會令人開心嘅地方」，若沒家人協助，不可能上車，年輕一代要考慮離開香港工作或定居，才有能力買樓。<br />\n<br />\n但他指，<span style=\"color: red;\">並非指年輕人應移居西方國家，「西方已經唔係過往20幾年人哋想像咁好」，尤其「美國夢其實已經係一個惡夢」，因當地中產25年來實質家庭收入無增長，與香港相約。他認為年輕人應考慮移居內地、印度、墨西哥、越南等地，便可從容地養妻活兒。<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170902&amp;guid=57161157&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170902%26guid%3D57161157%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=Ch1jav0lx7jvJrwEusI5hmMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=66edcb24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170902%26guid%3D57161157%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=299c315e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170902&amp;guid=57161157&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n連登仔最鍾意嘅移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4396a80d0e3610ca1c80458d6226dcc01681a30a","tid":384588,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T12:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17faf49ca3d07ece2cda2c6df2c2fff13e275048","tid":384588,"